# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Sandcastle Environment — Multi-Agent Setup
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# This project supports three AI agents via subscription or API key:
#   • Claude Code  — ANTHROPIC_API_KEY or subscription login (claude login)
#   • Codex        — OPENAI_API_KEY (or ~/.codex/config.toml)
#   • Kimi         — Subscription login (kimi login) or API key
#
# Only set the keys for the agent(s) you plan to use.
# Auth directories (e.g., ~/.claude, ~/.kimi) are auto-mounted into
# the sandbox when they exist, so subscription logins work transparently.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Claude Code ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional if you use `claude login` (subscription) — the ~/.claude
# directory is mounted into the sandbox automatically.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ─── Codex ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for Codex unless ~/.codex/config.toml is pre-configured.
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# ─── Kimi ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional if you use `kimi login` (subscription) — the ~/.kimi
# directory is mounted into the sandbox automatically.
# KIMI_API_KEY=...

# ─── Model Overrides ───────────────────────────────────────────
# MODEL=claude-opus-4-6
# MODEL=gpt-5.4
# MODEL=kimi-k2-0711-preview

# ─── Platform Overrides (auto-detected; set only if needed) ────
# SANDCASTLE_PROVIDER=docker        # docker | podman | vercel
# SANDCASTLE_AGENT=claude           # claude | codex | kimi
